Enum WfMessageType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WfMessageType>
      • org.whiteflag.protocol.core.WfMessageType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WfMessageType>

    public enum WfMessageType
extends java.lang.Enum<WfMessageType>
    Whiteflag message type

    This enumerable class implements the message types as defined in the Whiteflag standard. All message types have the same generic header. The message bodies are defined
